{
  "stem": "1677.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 88.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And every-- behind every of my project was always a nun and a bishop.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was my way to commemorate the happy days I had in my convent hiding time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Catholic Church, that was not the Australian administration-- and the Catholic Church had the money.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Catholic Church had the know-how.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Catholic Church was very powerful in Papua, New Guinea, very German, very Deutsche.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They're singing German-- sing songs at school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And these leprosy sisters send me a German video to our Jewish benefactor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Today, 25 years later, they still remember me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They are very wealthy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They make beautiful table mats.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there, I learned to do things for others.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I learned there community development.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I learned then-- the government send me to Israel on a scholarship, the, the six them-- Yom Kippur War broke out.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "As soon as I got there, the war was on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And President Katzir, because I helped the cause together very [? well-- ?] there were all blacks from Africa, from Sierra Leone, from the White Ivory Coast, from everywhere.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was representing Papua, New Guinea, a Kitty Fisher, a Jewish mama.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "When I came off the plane in Israel, the man who was sent to pick me up was from Tunis, to make it more difficult, spoke only French, no English.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He said [FRENCH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I said, Kitty Fisher.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I said, I am Kitty Fisher.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "No, no , no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[FRENCH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So there I was amongst all black savages, the only white Jewish woman during this dangerous time of the Yom Kippur War.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I listened to-- every night I got WIZO to come when they had a short-- when the news are on at 8:30, a terrible hour.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They came from the WIZO, two ladies.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
